title: #92Noon Nordo In For PA! Leber/Grimm/Korzo
description: Nordo is in for PA! We listen back to PA's interview with Mike Zimmer on X's and O's. Ben Leber makes his regular appearance, Gopher Football VOX Mike Grimm calls in to talk about the boat rowing, and Korzo is in studio!
